doc.after: During the long reign of Leopold I 1657 1705 and following the successful defense of Vienna in 1683 under the command of the King of Poland John III Sobieski 33 a series of campaigns resulted in bringing all of Hungary to Austrian control by the Treaty of Karlowitz in 1699
